text: Khanewal District () is a district in the Punjab province of Pakistan. The city of Khanewal is the capital. == District Government == The District is headed by a powering authority named as District Coordination Officer.Dco handles all developments and problem issues in whole District.EDO's work under DCO to cooperate in operations which are going on in District. ==Tehsils of Khanewal== * Kabirwala Tehsil * Khanewal Tehsil * Jahanian Tehsil * Mian Channu Tehsil Category:Khanewal District Category:Multan Division
title: Khanewal District
